arStrings.szText: I received a letter from Kyovashad. Another Iron Wolf has gone missingâ€”our youngest this time, Telan. A promising warrior, but too proud. If a demon tempts him with false promises, I fear he will not resist long.
You must save Telan from himself.  Look for him in the pine wilderness of the Fractured Peaks. He will be there, honing his skill, hunting for glory.
